<HEAD>231 Prisoners Released on King's Birthday</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KATMANDU, Nepal (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Prison officials released 231 inmates
serving sentences ranging from one month to 14 years, as part of
Friday's celebration of Kilambs: Choice and prime wooled and shorn with
no.1 and
2 pelts 100-110 lbs 58.00-60.00; 100-120 lbs 56.00-58.00; 120-130
lbs 52.00-56.00.
