   The dinner, held Friday night, is hosted each year by the Big 10
Club of Southern California. Other celebrities set to participate
in the fete include Claude Akins, Zsa Zsa Gabor, Jermaine Jackson,
Tommy Lasorda, Gavin MacLeod and McLean Stevenson.
   Entertainment is to be provided by comedian Norm Crosby,
impersonator George Kirby, Hope and Ms. Zadora. Rose Queen Yasmine
Delawari and her court are scheduled to be in attendance.
