<HEAD>ith Panama Bjt</HEAD>
<HEAD>U.S. Military Helped Envoy Return to Panama</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The papal envoy in Panama who has had Manuel
Antonio Noriega as a house guest since Sunday was out of the
country when the U.S. invasion occurred and was flown back to
Panama aboard a special U.S. military flight, American officials
said Friday.
   Archbishop Jose Sebastian Laboa, who has been a key figure in
