.58 to 194.17. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up .11 at 374.01.
   On Thursday the Dow Jones industrial average rose 7.90 to
2,732.30.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by about 5 to 4 on the
NYSE, with 835 up, 673 down and 469 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 128.03 million shares, against 133.73
million in the previous session.
